eth, and the sun goeth down, and hasteth to his place where he arose.","year":-977},{"id":"recD68v3tzDkH07ev","ref":"Eccl.1.6","text":"The wind goeth toward the south, and turneth about unto the north; it whirleth about continually, and the wind returneth again according to his circuits.","year":-977}]}
